---
/**
 * HeroScrollHint — línea vertical + chevron pulsante.
 * Reemplaza animate-bounce con un easing más sofisticado.
 */
---
<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-gold">
    <span>Bajá para descubrir</span>
    <span class="relative inline-flex h-7 w-3 items-center justify-center" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="absolute inset-x-1/2 top-0 h-3 w-px -translate-x-1/2 bg-brand-gold/50"></span>
        <span class="hero-scroll-chevron absolute bottom-0 inline-block leading-none">↓</span>
    </span>
</span>
